data.text:
published on 2024-07-07T19:57:41Z

WATCH (Highly Recommend) https://youtu.be/-EhNHlD-Oz8 I proudly present my biggest headline set to date. A 100 minuets of MPORT. The work that went into this show was above and beyond anything I've done before and I'm so pumped to have had it recorded. I made over 20 visuals, created many new songs, VIPs and of course the intro...my fave ever.. The main theme of this set surrounds my next EP, "Scene Selection." Where I take some of my favorite movies, memes and funny source material and transform it in to bangers. So anyway...blah..blah..blah.. Plug this into the loudest sound system you can find and enjoy!
